{"tid":1830972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[繼續送大禮] 南韓現首宗確診個案 支那女患者從武漢飛仁川 落機時發高燒","createTime":"2020-01-20T04:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T05:48:50.000Z","uid":26602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"490449a09ed19f26cc395a19d18148f914d0076a","tid":1830972,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:56:41.000Z","msg":"南韓聯合通訊社報道，南韓出現首宗確診個案，患者是一名來自中國武漢的中國藉女人，她從武漢飛仁川落機時發高燒。<br />\n<br />\n南韓疾病控制中心報告指，一名35歲的中國女子從中國武漢進入飛抵仁川國際機場，下機時已出現高燒和相關症狀，在仁川國際機場到達大廳即時被隔離，後來確診感染俗稱「武漢肺炎」的新型冠狀病毒。<br />\n<br />\n她稱上周曾在武漢遊覽，目前正在當地一間醫院接受治療。今次是繼日本和泰國之後，再有亞洲國家出現確診個案，患者都是中國人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200120/U5XOZDQDS34QTWIEC7VHVOSCQY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200120%2FU5XOZDQDS34QTWIEC7VHVOSCQY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=91fb2d3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200120%2FU5XOZDQDS34QTWIEC7VHVOSCQY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=62898066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200120/U5XOZDQDS34QTWIEC7VHVOSCQY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完仲唔載返口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b609cc4090568b4666362085bcaa5a2a57a99cc","tid":1830972,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"噢  成架機都係 ....."},{"pid":"12d29386332b0297201bc14c13ae44879d88efc1","tid":18309